. Bạn G&aacute;i Vs. Bạn Thời Thơ Ấu (2018)</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC55\"><strong>55. H&atilde;y Đi Đi, Xanh Biếc (2018)</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC56\"><strong>56. Thọ Mệnh Thế Giới V&agrave; Bảy Ng&agrave;y Đầu Ti&ecirc;n (2018)</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC57\"><strong>57. T&ocirc;i L&agrave; Nhện Đấy, C&oacute; Sao Kh&ocirc;ng? (2018)</strong></a></p>\r\n', 'Trains_daitoSchoolgirls_440648.jpg', '2018-12-13 11:19:58', '2018-12-13 04:19:23'),
(1, 'Những Light Novel đã được xuất bản ở Việt Nam', '<p><a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC1\"><strong>1. Tiểu thuyết Th&aacute;m tử lừng danh Conan (2012)</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC2\"><strong>2. C&acirc;u lạc bộ giỏi v&agrave; s&agrave;nh sỏi (2013)</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC3\"><strong>3. C&ocirc; G&aacute;i Văn Chương (2014)</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC4\"><strong>4. Suzumiya Haruhi (2014)</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC5\"><strong>5. 5 Centimet Tr&ecirc;n Gi&acirc;y (2014)</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC6\"><strong>6. Another (2015)</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC7\"><strong>7. Sword Art Online (2015)</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC8\"><strong>8. Ame V&agrave; Yuki - Những Đứa Con Của S&oacute;i (2015)</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC9\"><strong>9. Khu vườn ng&ocirc;n từ (2015)</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-du