(2, 'Những Light Novel đã được xuất bản ở Việt Nam 2', '<p><a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC16\"><strong>16. Cuốn s&aacute;ch của sự kết th&uacute;c (2016)</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC17\"><strong>17. B&iacute; Mật Giao Ước B&oacute;ng Tối (2016)&nbsp;</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC18\"><strong>18. Ph&aacute;p sư Tokyo (2016)&nbsp;</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC19\"><strong>19. Tiệm S&aacute;ch Cũ Biblia (2016-2017)&nbsp;</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC20\"><strong>20. Tiếng gọi từ v&igrave; sao xa (2016)&nbsp;</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC21\"><strong>21. Kem Đ&aacute; (2016-2017)&nbsp;</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC22\"><strong>22. Hiệp Sĩ Lưu Ban (2017)&nbsp;</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC23\"><strong>23. Orange - L&aacute; Thư Từ Tương Lai (2017)&nbsp;</strong></a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hako.re/forum/threads/nhung-light-novel-da-duoc-xuat-ban-o-viet-nam-ban-muon-ho-xuat-ban-bo-light-novel-nao.5328/#MOC24\"><strong>24. Cuộc Chiến Si&ecirc;u Nhi&ecirc;n Giữa Đời Thường (2017)&nbsp;</st